HEADWORD: Synastry
<hw>Syn"as*try</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>syn-</ets> + Gr. <?/ a star.]</ety> <def>Concurrence of starry
position or influence; hence, similarity of condition, fortune, etc., as
prefigured by astrological calculation.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Motley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
